What are you
doing here?

37:15.367 --> 37:17.067
Where you been?

37:17.069 --> 37:19.002
We were about to do
something horrible.

37:19.004 --> 37:20.670
Not we.

37:20.672 --> 37:22.372
Me. I was.

37:22.374 --> 37:24.207
I thought i knew
what was best.

37:24.209 --> 37:25.609
But i was wrong.

37:27.079 --> 37:28.178
I thought
the only way

37:28.180 --> 37:31.181
I could be happy...

37:31.183 --> 37:33.183
The only way
i could feel whole...

37:33.185 --> 37:35.752
Was to be separated
from my sister.

37:38.090 --> 37:39.923
I thought bette
was the problem.

37:41.693 --> 37:44.694
But she wasn't.

37:44.696 --> 37:46.296
It was me.

37:49.568 --> 37:52.035
My sweet...

37:52.037 --> 37:55.372
Sweet sister is
the purest part of my soul.

37:55.374 --> 37:58.208
We're a family.

37:58.210 --> 38:00.277
We belong together

38:00.279 --> 38:02.078
And i know that now.

38:02.080 --> 38:05.215
Well...

38:05.217 --> 38:07.284
Even family leaves.

38:09.221 --> 38:10.987
Nothing stays.

38:25.737 --> 38:28.405
I was so terribly sorry

38:28.407 --> 38:30.473
To hear about your mother.

38:32.477 --> 38:34.411
You're in such pain.

38:34.413 --> 38:37.247
I can feel it.

38:37.249 --> 38:39.349
But you're not alone.

38:40.485 --> 38:44.087
And you never have
to be alone again.

38:44.089 --> 38:46.489
What do you mean?

38:57.135 --> 38:59.269
Jimmy darling...

38:59.271 --> 39:01.604
I have loved you

39:01.606 --> 39:03.707
Since the first moment
i set eyes on you.

39:04.643 --> 39:06.776
You were warm

39:06.778 --> 39:09.946
And you were kind.

39:09.948 --> 39:11.281
And you looked right at me.

39:11.283 --> 39:13.316
You didn't flinch,

39:13.318 --> 39:15.285
Not even a bit.

39:15.287 --> 39:18.321
And in that moment,

39:18.323 --> 39:21.191
I felt i could face anything

39:21.193 --> 39:22.726
With you by my side.

39:33.505 --> 39:36.139
You are the only man for me.

39:36.141 --> 39:37.774
'cause you're like us.

39:39.211 --> 39:40.310
Different...

39:40.312 --> 39:42.579
But special.

39:45.650 --> 39:49.319
Let me take your pain away.

39:49.321 --> 39:51.388
Replace it with love.

39:53.992 --> 39:55.392
Dot...

39:57.396 --> 39:58.895
I don't know
what to say.

40:01.199 --> 40:03.199
Bette...

40:03.201 --> 40:06.236
Uh, how do you feel
about all this?

40:08.240 --> 40:10.407
I support dot.

40:10.409 --> 40:12.409
And dot wants you.

40:12.411 --> 40:14.344
Well...

40:14.346 --> 40:16.579
Well, it's your body, too.

40:16.581 --> 40:17.847
I can give you privacy.

40:17.849 --> 40:19.682
(laughs gently)
close my eyes

40:19.684 --> 40:22.352
And disappear
for a while.

40:22.354 --> 40:25.255
We could make you
so happy, jimmy.

40:25.257 --> 40:28.057
Not many men can boast

40:28.059 --> 40:31.094
Of a blonde and
a brunette for a wife.

40:51.550 --> 40:53.616
(gasps)

40:56.221 --> 40:57.787
Well, didn't you like it?

40:57.789 --> 41:00.590
Two souls, two mouths,

41:00.592 --> 41:02.892
Devoted only to you.

41:02.894 --> 41:05.462
To pleasing you.

41:05.464 --> 41:07.630
It could be that way always.

41:13.638 --> 41:15.305
I care about you.

41:17.976 --> 41:19.476
Both of you.

41:21.746 --> 41:24.314
But i can't.

41:34.659 --> 41:36.726
(sniffling)

41:39.464 --> 41:40.663
The truth is...

41:42.434 --> 41:45.201
...I'm in love
with someone else.

41:54.479 --> 41:57.080
She's a very lucky girl.

42:02.621 --> 42:04.587
We have to go.

42:32.150 --> 42:34.217
(crying quietly)

42:38.657 --> 42:40.723
(yells, bottle smashes)

42:42.694 --> 42:43.993
(sobs)

42:43.995 --> 42:46.462
(sirens approaching)

42:53.338 --> 42:54.737
Jimmy:
What the hell do you want?

42:54.739 --> 42:56.673
Jimmy darling,
you're under arrest...

42:56.675 --> 42:57.574
What?!

42:57.576 --> 42:58.841
...For the murders
of sylvia mills,

42:58.843 --> 43:00.176
Myrna austen,

43:00.178 --> 43:01.678
Joanne miller,

43:01.680 --> 43:03.413
And elaine seymour.
Wait, what?!

43:03.415 --> 43:04.681
Wait, i don't even know
those ladies.

43:04.683 --> 43:06.015
We have evidence.

43:06.017 --> 43:07.183
You left your glove

43:07.185 --> 43:09.352
At the crime scene,
lobster boy.

43:09.354 --> 43:10.553
What kind of sicko

43:10.555 --> 43:11.888
Goes after a bunch
of sweet housewives

43:11.890 --> 43:13.756
Just looking to buy
some tupperware?

43:13.758 --> 43:15.525
Wait, wait, wait,
you got it all wrong.

43:15.527 --> 43:16.759
I didn't...
I didn't do anything!

43:16.761 --> 43:18.361
No, he has been here
all day with me!

43:18.363 --> 43:19.362
You need to
back up.
This has to be...

43:19.364 --> 43:20.863
Back up!
(screams)
hey!

43:20.865 --> 43:22.699
Jimmy:
Do not touch her!
Where?

43:22.701 --> 43:24.567
You can't take him!
He didn't do anything!

43:24.569 --> 43:26.402
Jimmy:
I didn't do anything! Come on!

43:26.404 --> 43:27.403
(engine starts)

43:27.405 --> 43:29.405
Jimmy:
Maggie!

43:29.407 --> 43:32.375
Maggie!
(yells angrily)

43:32.377 --> 43:34.777
I didn't do nothing!

